Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.13,0:00:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always remember the day\Nmy younger sister first arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was as fragile as spring snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and hiding behind Mom, she cast her eyes\Ndown as she glanced at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From today, she's going to be your younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I smile, and reply, "Sure!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.37,0:00:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since, I haven't seen my younger sister at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, I brought your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll leave your meal right here.\NMake sure to eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:10.79,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(406.334,336.444)\frz14.68 \t(150,2700,\x105\y105)}Please come out of your room\Nso I can see your face.\N- From, Your Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Izumi Masamune .\NI'm a first year in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.32,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I go to school, but I also\Nwork as a light novel author.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I read your newest release!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey! Carry that a bit more carefully!\NThere's still a bit left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}From a year ago, I've been continually fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wanna try this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Against my younger sister\Nwho refuses to leave her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My irritation that I'm still\Nonly a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Izumi Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, all sorts of stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're sharp as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, the only family member left for me\Nis my little step-sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}From that incident a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}my younger sister shut herself in her room
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}and stopped communicating with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Come out of your room so I can see your face."\NThat is my only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.94,LeftSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(370.117,275.111)}Adachi Fourth Public High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The super-dangerous action that I sealed away\Nfrom the trauma I suffered after debuting...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.36,RightSignM,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(378.817,296)\frz343.1}Izumi Masamune Autograph Event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Egosurfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I debuted as a light novel author\Nright around when I entered middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And for the three years since,\Nmy trusty partner who draws really erotic art,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Silverwolf of Reincarnation 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eromanga-sensei, has been working with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}I really recommend this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have yet to meet this partner of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had my first autograph session\Ncommemorating the series completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:41.60,EpNum,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz341\pos(484.95,63.556)}"Silverwolf of Reincarnation"\NSeries Completion Commemoration\NAutograph Session - Author, Izumi Masamune
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.22,0:03:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}My pen name is also "Izumi Masamune".\NI just wrote my first name in katakana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I showed my face\Nduring the autograph session.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}So there's a chance my classmates\Nmight have realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm okay for no—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:00.80,DefaultC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(506.15,101.778)}[TERRIBLE NEWS] Izumi Masamune-sensei's\Nautograph is too messy lolololol
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on now,\Nstuff like that happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you ask me, it's the price of fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm really not that famous, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dissing someone like you, Mune-kun, isn't\Ngoing to increase page views on a blog, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomoe, what you're saying is even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mune-kun, Mune-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just looking at that post.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Isn't this the blog of the "sensei"\Nwho draws illustrations for your novels?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:32.06,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz342.8\pos(426.65,137.333)}Eromanga-sensei's Doodling Blog\N"At the Tip of the Panties"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is this guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Eromanga-sensei sure disses you\Nin a strangely happy fashion, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}The materials aren't here yet.\NThese settings are hard to understand!\NHe can write fast though (lol)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mune-kun, did you do something\Nto this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No! I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I mean, I haven't even met the guy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Despite working together for three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My editor said she's never met this guy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Apparently all the work\Nis done over the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A work style of the modern era!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe the guy found out\NI complained about the lewd pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you have to think about how I feel with\Neach cover showing "Art: Eromanga".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Mune-kun. Eromanga-sensei\Nis going to do live streaming later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A live streaming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah. I got it, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you're done eating,\Nleave the dishes outside the room!
