Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei, you sure changed\Nfrom about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, I used to do this\Nas an extension of my hobby.
