Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If not, I won't ever let you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you were streaming, the meal\NI made for you was in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You forgot to turn the camera off,\Nand you started taking your clothes off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's enough. I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So after all, Nii-san,\Nyou were "Izumi Masamune-sensei".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"After all"? You had noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was just thinking you had the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For it to actually be the same person...\NWhat kind of probability is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To think that I've been living under\Nthe same roof as Eromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, this is so sudden,\Nand I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For starters, I'm sorry\NI made you draw all those lewd pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't suddenly shout so loudly, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You're the idiot! Lewd pervert!\NEven the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your illustrations are really erotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't just say that to a girl, s-so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you have to get that angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was talking about how I was requesting\Nlewd illustrations from my younger sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Lewd illustrations are my job,\Nand I like it, so it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But you can't talk about stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, you idiot! Dunce!\NLight-novel protagonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fine. I won't say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's fine if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In the first place, Nii-san,\Nyou're all sorts of no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All sorts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,F-For instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's right!\NYou stay at home too much on days off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Writing is my side job,\Nso of course I'd be home working!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even during summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Back then, everything I wrote was getting\Nturned down, so I pulled a lot of all-nighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I forgot to make you meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The despair I felt when meals didn't arrive\Neven after thumping the floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...do you know how that feels, Nii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come out of your room and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think I've lost if I leave my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even if you say it like a famous quote,\Nit's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, I noticed\Nyou blog and stream stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not bad. But it was slightly unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You weren't the person I knew,\Nand you were really lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's fun. Drawing art, and chatting\Nwith everyone while streaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want to hear more stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hardly know anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason why I started drawing illustrations\Nwas because Mom taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was naturally doing nothing but drawing\Nsince I was little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I was a professional before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom complimented me,\Nsaying it was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After Mom was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I couldn't draw at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I couldn't leave my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But one day, I saw someone streaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That person was happily drawing\Nwhile chatting with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted to be like that, and tried it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After seeing the illustrations, they give me\Ntheir opinions, like "so cute", "so amazing".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They ask me to draw more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm still in my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I can play and chat with people\Nall over the world like we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That, really, really makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. It's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The reason I became an author
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,was because the people posting their novels\Non the internet seemed to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There was a time when I wrote novels\Non the web, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, I got my first fan mail ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:23.04,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs14\an8\frz20.02\pos(439.9,280)}That was a great story!I drew a picture of \Nthe Hero Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That made me so happy.\NI was really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why I'm here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(481.417,12.889)}The Adventures of Hero Masamune\NCongrats on the Completion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder if that person\Nstill reads my novels today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see, so Izumi-sensei, you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, n-nothing!\NI knew you wrote novels on the web!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I see. But to think I'd see the day\Nwhere I could talk to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, why are you bothering me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You should just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do I trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's because you're my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And Mom asked me to take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that your reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I still don't know what counts\Nas taking good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I just do things that I feel\Nwould count as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Other than that, I'm just lonely, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'd like to eat meals together\Nwith my cute younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And I want to take care of her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even a troublesome younger sister like this,\Nwho hardly ever talks to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So you were aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I want us to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because we're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are we a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course. We live together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see. I don't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't call people\Nmerely living together a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want to talk anymore.\NGet out, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This illustration made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together next time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How stupid. That was something\NI only drew out of a sense of obligation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.47,0:23:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Jinno Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is Sagiri-chan here?
